}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
As the flavor index to represent the wave number is missing, the flavor \
indices are inconsistent. Therefore, the spin is regarded as 0.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1283656218,ExpressionUUID->"272540cc-4205-43df-8306-fa5da739cd46"],

